In Chaf1a  /  E4 embryos , which are arrested between the eight - and 16-cell stage , DAPI-dense foci were barely detectable ( Figure 1D ) .
Instead , DAPI staining was diffuse within the nucleus , with regions of higher density around the nucleoli and at the periphery of the nuclei ( Figure 1D ) .
